Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.40,0:00:20.30,OpLetraN5,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Enquanto olhava para o céu,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.30,0:00:24.33,OpLetraN5,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}me perguntei se você ainda se lembrava.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.33,0:00:31.43,OpLetraN5,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Daquelas estações que vimos passar, repletas de sentimentos incertos.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.33,0:00:36.30,OpLetraN5,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Se essa memória puder se tornar
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.30,0:00:39.26,OpLetraN5,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}um fragmento no canto do seu coração,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.26,0:00:44.21,OpLetraN5,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}eu espero que o seu sorriso,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.21,0:00:48.30,OpLetraN5,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}possa permanecer em seu devido lugar.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.30,0:00:52.33,OpLetraN5,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Se o tempo continuar passando,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.33,0:00:56.36,OpLetraN5,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}e eu puder permanecer aqui com você,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.36,0:00:59.76,OpLetraN5,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}tenho a sensação de que um dia veremos
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.76,0:01:03.53,OpLetraN5,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}mundos nunca vistos antes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.53,0:01:08.20,OpLetraN5,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Se um dia essas palavras forem comunicadas,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.20,0:01:12.36,OpLetraN5,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}para evitar que caiam em direção ao céu,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.36,0:01:18.26,OpLetraN5,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}vamos pegar essas memórias que deixamos escondidas
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.26,0:01:23.46,OpLetraN5,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}e guardá-las em nosso baú de tesouros.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.40,0:00:20.30,OpRomajiN5,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Utsuro ni sora mita
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.30,0:00:24.33,OpRomajiN5,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Kimi wa mada oboeteru kana
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.33,0:00:31.43,OpRomajiN5,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Misukoshita kisetsu mo futashika na kanjou de
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.33,0:00:36.30,OpRomajiN5,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Kokoro no sumikko demo
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.30,0:00:39.26,OpRomajiN5,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Kakera ni nareta nara
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.26,0:00:44.21,OpRomajiN5,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Kimi no ano egao ga
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.21,0:00:48.30,OpRomajiN5,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Arubeki basho ni aru to ii na
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.30,0:00:52.33,OpRomajiN5,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Kono jikan ga sugite yuku nara
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.33,0:00:56.36,OpRomajiN5,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Kimi to tomo ni irareta no nara
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.36,0:00:59.76,OpRomajiN5,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Mita koto no nai sekai
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.76,0:01:03.53,OpRomajiN5,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Mirareru you na ki ga shite
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.53,0:01:08.20,OpRomajiN5,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Itsuka kono kotoba mo tsutawaru no nara
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.20,0:01:12.36,OpRomajiN5,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Sora e ochite shimawanu you ni
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.36,0:01:18.26,OpRomajiN5,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Dokoka no ura ni nokoshita omoide mo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.26,0:01:23.46,OpRomajiN5,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Takarabako ni shimatte
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.93,0:22:11.62,EdLetraN5,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}As folhas caídas balançam no canto da esquina.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.62,0:22:19.40,EdLetraN5,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Um vento seco está soprando
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.40,0:22:25.90,EdLetraN5,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}e passando pela rua principal, longe da multidão.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.90,0:22:34.62,EdLetraN5,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Indo até um local distante, onde ninguém está.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.62,0:22:45.70,EdLetraN5,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Eu fingi não ter percebido, mesmo sabendo que
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.70,0:22:57.10,EdLetraN5,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}completamente sozinha, não havia nada que eu pudesse fazer.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.43,0:23:04.30,EdLetraN5,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Me despedi dos fantasmas que conheci,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.30,0:23:10.46,EdLetraN5,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}em direção àquele céu vermelho.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.46,0:23:17.23,EdLetraN5,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Em meio a minha fraqueza, eu estendo minha mão,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.23,0:23:24.33,EdLetraN5,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}como se estivesse segurando uma flor que não desabrochou.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.33,0:23:34.53,EdLetraN5,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Enquanto novos encontros acontecem, realizo meu desejo.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.93,0:22:11.62,EdRomajiN5,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Kareha mau machikado wo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.62,0:22:19.40,EdRomajiN5,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}kakenuketeku kawaita kaze
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.40,0:22:25.90,EdRomajiN5,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Menukidoori hitonami nukete
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.90,0:22:34.62,EdRomajiN5,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Dokoka tooku daremo inai basho e
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.62,0:22:45.70,EdRomajiN5,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Kizuite ita noni nanimo shiranai furi
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.70,0:22:57.10,EdRomajiN5,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Hitori kiri de wa nanimo dekinakatta
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.43,0:23:04.30,EdRomajiN5,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Deaeta maboroshi ni sayonara wo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.30,0:23:10.46,EdRomajiN5,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Akane sasu kono sora ni
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.46,0:23:17.23,EdRomajiN5,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Koboreta yowasa ni tenohira wo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.23,0:23:24.33,EdRomajiN5,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Hitohira no hanabira sonna fuu ni
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.33,0:23:34.53,EdRomajiN5,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Deai kasane negai o shiru
